blacklist.reply2:
`\`🛡️\` **Blacklist** is a feature that **prevents freshly created accounts from joining your server**. New accounts are often **bots, scams and adverts** that could be used maliciously to **harm your server users**.

Blacklist is **activated by default**, you can change the times according to **your needs**:
> \`Blacklist length: ${this.client.PrettyMs(blacklistTime,{verbose: true})}\` ${blacklistTime == 86400000 ? ' (default)' : ''}
> ↪ *change how long the bot will block the newcomer for.*> \`Account age required: ${this.client.PrettyMs(blacklistMinAge, {verbose: true})}\` ${blacklistMinAge == 3600000 ? ' (default)' : ''}
> ↪ *change the minimum age a newcomer must be to join the server.*
\`⏱️\` To change the blacklist times, please use, \`/setup blacklist\` command.`
